Look who is wearing AirVuz gear! Repost from @queen_of_the_drone using @RepostRegramApp - Teaching one of my besties @muxymae how to fly!!! How exciting to have a fellow #dronie here to fly with! I even let her fly my Mavic! First person to ever fly one of the Queens princesses! Haha! She's a natural! I was happy to help make her feel more comfortable in flight so when she travels around the world she can get that new perspective on camera! Im a proud friend! I'm gathering some sweet footage of me in my new @airvuz gear! I looooove representing game changing companies!The @djiglobal #djispark is such a cute little thing! Using the phone as the controller is different, yet very user friendly and easy to learn. All in all, I'm a fan and will definitely be adding this to my gear list. #naturaldronie #dronelife #dronestagram #unitedbydrone #dronenerds #dronegear #chicksthatdrone #dronechicks #letsdrone #motivated #motivationmonday #spark #girltime #sundayfunday
